<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/housing-ombudsman> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Housing Ombudsman Service (HOS) looks at complaints about registered providers of social housing, for example housing associations, and other landlords, managers and agents. The service is free, independent and impartial. HOS is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government ."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
